netradiant (1.5.0+20220629+1-0wjd1+REL) stable; urgency=medium

  * Update upstream.
  * Move source files around into ./source-files/.
  * Moved the tools from /usr/bin to to libdir. This way we don't need to
    Conflict with GtkRadiant or NRC (nrcradiant) anymore.
  * Moved q3.game docs to /usr/share/doc/netradiant. Now the local manual can
    be opened using sandboxed/restricted browsers.

 -- Walter Doekes <wjdoekes+netradiant@osso.nl>  Sat, 16 Jul 2022 23:05:49 +0200

